headline.main: SINGAPORE'S GUNS LAUNCH DEFENSE; Japanese Attacked as They Seek to Establish Line Opposite Island SINGAPORE'S GUNS LAUNCH DEFENSE

lead_paragraph: SINGAPORE, Feb. 1 -- Singapore's guns along the low north shore today opened fire for the first time in direct defense of this principal Far Eastern British base, sending their shells screaming across the Strait of Johore.
